# ── Phantom junk files ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Zero-byte files created when JS/TS/CSS fragments get executed in a shell and
# `>` redirects a token to a file (e.g. an AI/codex session pasting code).
# All patterns are root-anchored (leading /) so they can NEVER match real
# source like docs/design/. If a new fragment shape appears, add it here.
/[({][!-~]*
/,*
/*.,+
/0
/3
/design
/span
/helpedAt
/transcribe-note
/weekStart.getTime()
/a.due_at
/assignment.id
/window.clearInterval(id)

# Backend export bundles (generated)
/export/
